{"tid":494862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登玩具雞開單 港男被騙10萬","createTime":"2017-12-10T06:25:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-10T11:30:40.000Z","uid":130894,"like":105,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"83dac9dc76fbace299168fa2cceb59ee270442c4","tid":494862,"uid":130894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T06:25:47.000Z","msg":"一名姓黃31歲男子，早前在交友程式認識一名女子，雙方結識了幾個月。近日該女子幾次致電男事主聲稱被人捉走，要求他付贖金。<br />\n<br />\n男事主不虞有詐，購買約值10萬港元的比特幣，並轉帳至一個戶口，但事後仍未能聯絡該女子，懷疑遇到騙案，凌晨零時許在慈雲山中心報警。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20171210&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=57562451【比特幣電騙】女網友聲稱被捉走\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171210%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D57562451%E3%80%90%E6%AF%94%E7%89%B9%E5%B9%A3%E9%9B%BB%E9%A8%99%E3%80%91%E5%A5%B3%E7%B6%B2%E5%8F%8B%E8%81%B2%E7%A8%B1%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%89%E8%B5%B0&d=ePCWnjtSfoUi8ES%2FkCpDSzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=aec90b0d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171210%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D57562451%E3%80%90%E6%AF%94%E7%89%B9%E5%B9%A3%E9%9B%BB%E9%A8%99%E3%80%91%E5%A5%B3%E7%B6%B2%E5%8F%8B%E8%81%B2%E7%A8%B1%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%89%E8%B5%B0&h=868db665\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20171210&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=57562451【比特幣電騙】女網友聲稱被捉走</a> 男子被呃10萬元Bitcoin<br />\n<br />\n其實而家真係愈來愈多we7雞同line雞去呃香港啲傻鳩  雖然我哋祝展強集團已經努力每日撚鳩佳佳，但騙徒手法層岀不窮，我係呢度呼籲各位巴打如果遇到其他集團既詐騙雞，請繼續放上黎一齊研究<br />\n90年代香港遍地黃金，而家香港遍地傻鳩<br />\n科技愈高智能，人類愈低能<br />\n再係咁落去，香港只會變成支那人爭相落黎詐騙既地方<br />\n因為精蟲上腦嘅港男，太易水了~"},{"pid":"20066ee1b33cb6ba4d82269cbfcf72aa249bf692","tid":494862,"uid":130894,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T06:33:24.000Z","msg":"佳佳都係呃千三<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俾人呃6位數真係on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"360ead61616d598d4eb4756a5d3763ea256e4c3a","tid":494862,"uid":46759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T06:35:07.000Z","msg":"有上連登就唔使做侵鳩啦"},{"pid":"80e2ba19bfe618e0fedf54cafe56088367bd2704","tid":494862,"uid":36502,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T07:50:13.000Z","msg":"識上連登，就唔洗比佳佳厄左10萬啦"},{"pid":"90d2eaff26afc440f0e0641fc45945f8af6723c0","tid":494862,"uid":130894,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T07:56:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有上連登就唔使做侵鳩啦</blockquote><br />\n所以其實好慘，不如唔好加密，由啲小學雞玩，咁至少可以擊退啲騙徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfdd0d63fead238883f450913a921a6af0b5ba8c","tid":494862,"uid":130894,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T07:58:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>識上連登，就唔洗比佳佳厄左10萬啦</blockquote><br />\n以前就話啲祈福黨可以呃啲啊婆<br />\n點解今時今日咁撚大個男人可以俾人呃到幾十個？"},{"pid":"d70e1e47db8a5777cdd1359ecf4a9e89736a4277","tid":494862,"uid":52946,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T07:59:21.000Z","msg":"安安平時做晒宣傳都有人比佳佳水到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f8950f0be07264a7da52c15a1316f7b6412ebde","tid":494862,"uid":130894,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T08:02:58.000Z","msg":"點解精蟲上腦到咁？<br />\n點解要幻想有英雄救美呢啲嘢係世界發生？就算真係有，其實都唔會係佢<br />\n點解個人咁撚蠢都有十萬俾人呃，我咁撚醒就只能用11蚊買豬柳強<br />\n佳佳係S5話香港好多傻鳩果下我真係心都碎埋，幾時開始，連雞都睇我地唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32d41df245bd4540d878740e7108029d1f97dd2c","tid":494862,"uid":49163,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T08:03:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c45d60ded853913495ec1c3ceeb37b7a5b5116b8","tid":494862,"uid":130894,"like":1,"di